      "DialogueText_10_10D44AC44144EC85326507BD9E2D1C2A": "NSLOCTEXT(\"\", \"DD69C6DC40181A857C5D2C9D00286B98\", \"I have planted these recordings inside Roland, using his memory framework. Though, they\\'re not really memories... Just hidden messages, triggered when certain conditions are met.\")",
